&lt;p&gt;The Commissioning Manager will lead and coordinate commissioning activities across Aypa’s portfolio of utility-scale Battery Energy Storage Systems (BESS), Solar PV, and hybrid projects. This role is highly cross-functional, interfacing with construction, engineering, operations, and external vendors to ensure safe, timely, and compliant commissioning of assets.&lt;/p&gt;
