&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead commissioning efforts across multiple project sites, ensuring alignment with contractual, technical, and regulatory requirements;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with EPC vendors, OEMs, subcontractors, AHJs, and grid operators to plan and execute commissioning activities;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and validate commissioning test results and documentation from contractors and vendors;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure completeness and accuracy of turnover packages;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and maintain standardized commissioning templates and tools to streamline workflows and reduce repetitive effort;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Procurement, Pre-Construction, and Construction teams to review commissioning exhibits in contracts and support project execution;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel to project sites during critical commissioning phases to oversee testing and troubleshoot issues;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the handoff of commissioned assets to the Operations team, ensuring readiness and documentation compliance;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties as required or assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
